{"id": "art-25157", "label": "Art. 25157", "title": "Art. 25157", "slug": "art-25157", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_863915313\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1375\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_863915313\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>57</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_130459579\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1374\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_130459579\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Administratorii sau, dup&#259; caz, membrii consiliului\nde <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> ori ai directoratului\nr&#259;spund solidar, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 73, pentru prejudiciul cauzat prin fapta lor culpabil&#259; în\nîndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span> prev&#259;zute de <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> în cadrul procedurilor de derulare\na transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1270147227\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1373\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1270147227\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Exper&#355;ii</span> care întocmesc\nraportul prev&#259;zut la art. 251<sup>45</sup>, pe seama <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nce face obiectul transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere, r&#259;spund solidar\npentru prejudiciul cauzat prin fapta lor culpabil&#259; în îndeplinirea <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span> prev&#259;zute de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>lege</i> în cadrul procedurilor de derulare a transform&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere.</span></p>"}